query:
INSERT INTO app.projects (
                name,
                visibility,
                crs_srid,
                owner,
                added_by,
                last_updated_by,
                slug,
                team_id
            )
            VALUES( $1, $2, $3, $4, $4, $4, $5, (SELECT team_id from app.users WHERE id =$4 ))

            RETURNING id AS "id: ProjectId"
